{
  "stem": "19690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, just about this time, my mother started to have clothing made for us-- for herself, for my father, and me-- for immigration, because they were thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And everything that she had made had a lot of extra material in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And this is part of where I say my mother was a very smart woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Some of these clothes I wore until I came to the United States in 1946, because she had so much extra material in the waist and in the length that they could just keep letting out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And she had clothes made for herself that would do double or triple duty-- skirts with jackets and vests so she could wear it formally or informally, wherever she was.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my-- my father had some extra suits made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And there too, they were of material that was very durable and neutral colors, so that they could work in any environment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And this was '38 and in '39.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother had a sister who already lived in the United States, who immigrated in 1937.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the time, they were called crazy for leaving and selling their business.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole family was in an uproar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're crazy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They don't know what they're doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're leaving a good business for a country where there is a recession-- depression, in fact.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were the only smart ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then, all of a sudden, it became, we have to find someone who can get us an affidavit to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Since we had no other relatives and these-- my aunt and uncle were struggling-- they couldn't provide for us-- and they started looking for other relatives.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
